balanceOf(address).details: Calculates how many shares a user holds.

batchOperateOnExchange(address,(bytes)[].details: Allows owner or approved exchange to send a transaction to exchangeWith data of signed/unsigned transaction

buyDrago().details: Allows a user to buy into a drago.

buyDragoOnBehalf(address).details: Allows a user to buy into a drago on behalf of an address.

calcSharePrice().details: Returns the price of a pool.
calcSharePrice().return: Value of the share price in wei.

changeDragoDao(address).details: Allows drago dao/factory to upgrade its address.

params._dragoDao: Address of the new drago dao.

changeFeeCollector(address).details: Allows owner to decide where to receive the fee.

changeMinPeriod(uint32).details: Allows drago dao/factory to change the minimum holding period.

changeRatio(uint256).details: Allows drago dao/factory to change fee split ratio.

params._ratio: Number of ratio for wizard, from 0 to 100.

getAdminData().details: Finds the administrative data of the pool.
getAdminData().return: Address of the account where a user collects fees.Address of the drago dao/factory.Number of the fee split ratio.Value of the transaction fee in basis points.Number of the minimum holding period for shares.

getData().details: Finds details of a drago pool.
getData().return: String name of a drago.String symbol of a drago.Value of the share price in wei.Value of the share price in wei.

getEventful().details: Gets the address of the logger contract.

isValidSignature(bytes32,bytes).details: Verifies that a signature is valid.

operateOnExchange(address,(bytes)).details: Allows owner to operate on exchange through extension.

sellDrago(uint256).details: Allows a user to sell from a drago.

setAllowance(address,address,uint256).details: Allows owner to set an allowance to an approved token transfer proxy.

params._amount: Number of tokens approved for spending.
params._token: Address of the token to receive allowance for.
params._tokenTransferProxy: Address of the proxy to be approved.

setMultipleAllowances(address,address[],.details: Allows owner to set allowances to multiple approved tokens with one call.

params._amounts: Array of number of tokens to be approved.
params._tokenTransferProxy: Address of the proxy to be approved.
params._tokens: Address of the token to receive allowance for.

setPrices(uint256,uint256,uint256,bytes3.details: Allows drago owner or authority to set the price for a drago.

params._signaturevaliduntilBlock: Number of blocks till expiry of new data.

setTransactionFee(uint256).details: Allows drago owner to set the transaction fee.

params._transactionFee: Value of the transaction fee in basis points.

totalSupply().details: Returns the total amount of issued tokens for this drago.
